	<p style="color:#ff3300;">
	WARNING: Use this pages with care. It bypass the checking.
	</p>
	<div style="padding:5px;">
	
	1. 	Edit grouping, after the group is used and student already started evaluating. 
		<ul>
		<li>- Go the edit grouping page</li>
		<li>- add the word "admin" into the URL.  
			<br/>
			eg: From <em>/webapp/modules/group/edit/1722662626273</em> to <em>/webapp/modules/group/edit<strong>admin</strong>/1722662626273</em>
			<a href="${context:lib/ss/ss2-editgroup.jpg}" target="_blank" style="padding-left:15px;">Picture1 </a>
			<br/>
			eg: From <em>/webapp/modules/group/enrolluser/1722662626273</em> to <em>/webapp/modules/group/enrolluser<strong>admin</strong>/1722662626273</em>
			<a href="${context:lib/ss/ss1-enrolluser.jpg}" target="_blank"  style="padding-left:15px;">Picture2 </a>
			
		</li>
		</ul>
	 </div>
	 ---------------------
	<div style="padding:5px;">
	
	2. 	Delete Student's Evaluated grades 
		<ul>
		<li>- Go the view grade by evaluator</li>
		<li>- add the word "admin" into the URL.  
			<br/>
			eg: From <em>/webapp/modules/peerevaluation/viewdetailbyassessor/48366333/223334</em> to <em>/webapp/modules/peerevaluation/viewdetailbyassessor<strong>admin</strong>/48366333/223334</em>
			<a href="${context:lib/ss/ss3-deletedEvaulatedGrade.jpg}" target="_blank" style="padding-left:15px;">Picture3 </a>			
